sentences.english: They returned in turn to bury the luxuries burnt in the burst.
sentences.chinese: 他們順次返返來埋躲在爆炸中銷燬的豪侈品。

sentences.english: These in descending order of similar data element set is called array.
sentences.chinese: 這些順次擺列地同類數據元素地匯合稱爲數組。

sentences.english: In this paper, the properties of vertex-neighbor-integrity of sequential-joined graphs are discussed.
sentences.chinese: 討論了順次聯圖鄰域完整度的一些性質。

sentences.english: When the fish were added one at a time, people perceived the evidence to be stronger.
sentences.chinese: 當魚被一種一種地順次放入時，人們認爲證據更有力。

sentences.english: Even when services are unrelated to one another, they're still started one after the other.
sentences.chinese: 即使這些服務彼此無關時，依然會順次啓動它們。
